    "default_locale": "en-US",
    "description": {
        "en-US": "<b>If button texts were not aligned, please, change default font and size.<b>\n\n<b>Please, use browserAction to put it at toolbartoolbar or menubar.</b>\n<b>Please, put browserAction at mail toolbar, when not using button.</b>\n<b>Soon, if calendaring APIs completed, I will update this program^^.</b> \n\nExecuted well.\n\n<b>[Notes]\nI know you are inconvenient using browserAction button. As of the present, TaskviewStyles button can be positioned at task toolbar(2) in a form of the past instead of browserAction. I consider whether I wait future browserAction upgrade or I return it to the past form which is possible in my technical scope now.</b></b></b>"
    },
